as artificial grass around the pool area--maybe to keep up the grassy appearance during winter.Overall a nice place. We were in town visiting relatives, so being on the Strip wasn't important to us-- otherwise it would've been more hectic driving all around. The resort has more of a 'local' feel to it since it's away from the strip. We would probalbly stay there again--if the price is right!	
